query:
SELECT 
  pl.id,
  pl.labelCode,
  pl.productId,
  pl.productSku,
  pl.batch,
  p.description as productName
FROM productLabels pl
LEFT JOIN products p ON pl.productId = p.id
WHERE pl.labelCode = '22D08LB108'
LIMIT 5;
